@track ALM_14B_EVAL
@state pending
@date 2026-04-17
@file training/eval_alm_14b.hexa training/eval_alm_13b.hexa

@gate hire_sim_lenient >= 0.90
@gate tool_use_gate >= 0.85
@gate phi_holo >= 1000
@gate sample_gen 10KO+10EN qualitative

@decision A2_eval >= 0.93 → skip 13B → 70B direct
@decision A2_eval [0.85,0.93) → fire 13B de-risk ($36/12h)
@decision A2_eval < 0.85 → HALT

@chain ←alm_14b_a2_tool.convergence →alm_13b.convergence | alm_70b.convergence
